  "title": "Api proposal: currentRefinementsList widget",
  "body": "The goal is to be able to list the current refinement and delete them one by one or all at one time.\n\nExample from Jadopado :\n\n![capture d ecran 2015-09-22 a 11 48 39](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1689007/10015385/205abb20-6120-11e5-8c5c-2923f71f6f3d.png)\n\n```\nsearch.addWidget(\n instantsearch.widgets.currentRefinementsList({\n    container: '#current-refinements',\n    //clearAllButon // true or false\n    //template\n })\n);\n```\n\nResulting dom would look something like:\n\n```\n<div id='current-refinements'>\n  <div>Clear All</div>\n  <div>\n     <div>Men <span>x</span></div>\n     <div>Nike <span>x</span></div>\n</div>\n```\n\nWhat do you think ?\n",
